Package: netcopula
Type: Package
Title: Copula-Based Model for Multivariate Network Meta-Analysis (NMA)
Version: 0.1.4
Date: 2019-12-11
Authors@R: c(
	person("Sergio", "Venturini", role=c("aut", "cre"), email = "sergio.venturini@unito.it"),
	person("Rebecca", "Graziani", role=c("aut"), email = "rebecca.graziani@unibocconi.it"))
Author: Sergio Venturini [aut, cre],
    Rebecca Graziani [aut]
Maintainer: Sergio Venturini <sergio.venturini@unito.it>
Description: Methods for fitting a copula-based model for multivariate network
    meta-analysis within a fully Bayesian framework. Currently, it includes methods
    only for binary data.
